	   <tr><td colspan=2>&quot;Crusador Vragor&quot; in TT said something about this.&nbsp;&nbsp;To get the entire quest from him, all you need is the last line. . . But to go in order, &quot;Hail&quot; him. then say &quot;no&quot; then say &quot;yes&quot; . . .its that lame.  BUT. . . here is what he sais when you say &quot;yes&quot; (his last line). . .<br><br><br>&quot;I will tell you but you must help me first.  i have been tied to this plane because of deeds unfinished.  I was questing for the _stupendous tome_ for ages to no avail.  Without this tome i can not pass on in peace.  Finish my quest, bring me the _stupendous tome_ and _a crusador coffin_.  I will tell you where the beast rests before I pass on.  I doubt you will finish this, but I can always hope.&quot;<br><br><br>This item is indeed a quest item... give this and the stupendous tome to Crusador Vragor, and he will tell you.  If you say &quot;no&quot; to him, he Talks about this Master Tynn who meditated then froze in meditaion, so this Trakanasaur ate him, but he was so frozen the Trak swalloed him whole.  &quot;To this day he wanders with them lodged in his stomach.  Are you interested in knowing where Zhaoku is?&quot;  is the last sentanece of his thing. The Trak's name is Zhaoku.<br><br>So here is what is needed, to find this Zhaoku, since he still wanders 'to this day'.  Mostlikely, finishing the quest with Vragor spawns him, but thats a different quest.  Zhaoku probably drops the remains of this Tynn fella. . . who.. *shrug* i dunno.<br><br>We need to find this Stupendous tome first. . . in order to get Zhaoku's location.  Anyone ever heard of a stupendous tome?  <br><br><br><br>BTW Vragor  wasin TT at the EJ zone line, he didnt move for a long while, so i dont know if thats his spawn and hes stays.. or if he roams and spawns somewhere else.  Many peeps tried to attack him, he hits for 168 max i believe, and fast enough.  This was against a 60 paladin.  The paly used lay Hands, and throughout all that time, he still couldn't even dent his HP.  He is level 60 (the mob), even to 60's.<br>&nbsp;<br>0_o</td></tr>
